---
title: Cheesy Shredded BBQ Beef Subs with Horseradish-Dressed Coleslaw
description: If you love a cheesesteak sandwich, prepare to have a new favourite! These quick beef subs are sauced up with smoky-sweet BBQ sauce and loaded with cheese before a quick broil in the oven to reach gooey, melty perfection.
